%global packname  PabonLasso
%global packver   1.0
%global rlibdir   /usr/local/lib/R/library

Name:             R-CRAN-%{packname}
Version:          1.0
Release:          2%{?dist}
Summary:          Pabon Lasso Graphs and Comparing Situations of a Unit in TwoDifferent Times

License:          GPL (>= 2)
URL:              https://cran.r-project.org/package=%{packname}
Source0:          %{url}&version=%{packver}#/%{packname}_%{packver}.tar.gz


BuildRequires:    R-devel
Requires:         R-core
BuildArch:        noarch

%description
Pabon Lasso is a graphical method for monitoring the efficiency of
different wards of a hospital or different hospitals.Pabon Lasso graph is
divided into 4 parts which are created after drawing the average of BTR
and BOR. The part in the left-down side is Zone I, left-up side is Zone
II, Right-up side part is Zone III and the last part is Zone IV.

